1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
So when the manager approached her, his face grim, she felt well-steeled to deal with his complaints.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:07,600
Only when his words sank in did her smile begin to fade.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,400
The ghost, he said. It's Vavok.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,800
The ramp he was digging to the underground lake must have collapsed.

5
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:18,400
His voice faded into noise, his mouth moving, but few of the words penetrating Cole's shock.

6
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:21,600
No body, Cole heard. We can only guess what happened.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,000
They engraved a memorial slab, of course.

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Cole stood before it, still in shock.


